## Usage <a name="usage"></a>

Importing collapse module:

```typescript
import { CollapseModule } from 'ng2-bootstrap/ng2-bootstrap';
```
The collapse component uses these classes to handle content folding:

`.collapse` hides the content
`.collapse.in` shows the content
`.collapsing` used during expand/collapse starts/finishes
